Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:44.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100580,104792}Then you also went\Nto the fortune teller Pandora…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105335,106502}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:50.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106502,110632}And when I came to, the ring,\Nour family heirloom, was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111132,113092}{\i1}It's the same trick as the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113593,116596}But, Sister! I'm sure of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116596,119432}The one who stole\Nthe ring is St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120433,122393}There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:08.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124145,128399}Mom's Enemy!\NRosemary's Conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:15.82,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:133321,135823}{\fad(500,0)}Serial robbery by Saint Tail continues
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:20.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136491,140286}This is the longest\Nit's gone in Seika City's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:26.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140787,146167}I've heard that all of the victims\Nare saying St. Tail did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146334,148044}{\i1}I don't know anything about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148753,150505}What a terrible thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150505,153466}My dad says he can't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154258,156010}{\i1}I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158429,161307}There's no way that\Nshe would do these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175405,176614}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177699,178491}A warning note…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179450,182453}St. Tail's warning note\Nhasn't been delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:09.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184789,189168}We had an agreement that she would\Ngive me a warning note every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189168,191754}She's never broken the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193423,194924}{\i1}Promise…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195174,196926}Those newspaper articles…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:18.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197969,198886}I don't believe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203558,206060}{\i1}Thank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211065,213776}It has to be hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:40.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215027,220241}All of the victims are made to believe\Nthat St. Tail stole their things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221868,224704}That's the revenge\Non the Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224704,228249}{\i1}In order to get revenge on my mom,\Nshe's giving me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228249,229208}{\i1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229208,230460}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231085,235131}Even though I thought it was\Ndisrespectful to your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:58.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235131,238926}I researched the old articles\Nabout Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243139,244432}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.60,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:242138,245600}Thief Lucifer publicly\Nchallenges Rosemary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:10.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246350,250229}It looks like Mysterious\NThief Lucifer's warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250229,252315}Oh, Mom. What a showoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:19.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253191,259030}In this article, Rosemary seemed\Nto be Lucifer's opponent, I mean, rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259572,261616}Yeah. I heard\Nabout her from Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261616,263618}She was like a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264035,267789}The person who resents Lucifer\Ncan only be this same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267789,271834}You're right. Mom returned\Nall of the items she had stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:37.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272710,277799}{\i1}But this Rosemary has\Nsome connection with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278674,282303}I'm going to Pandora again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282303,285139}I may find the location\Nof the victim's ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287475,290478}By the way, Seira,\Nhow do you pronounce this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.62,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:306118,307620}Fortune Telling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308162,310540}{\i1}I'm really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310540,312416}{\i1}If the same thing\Nhappens to me again…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314669,315545}{\i1}But I have to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316128,319006}{\i1}For the sake\Nof St. Tail's reputation…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320800,322468}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328975,331143}Welcome!\NI've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.64,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:331143,332645}{\fad(300,0)}Pandora's Original Goods\NMedusa Chan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:38.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333604,338609}You don't need to be\Nthat surprised! Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347118,348286}{\i1}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351455,352707}{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355209,357295}How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357295,359130}Mom! You've got\Nto get rid of that habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360673,361716}You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361716,364594}You look exactly like\NLucifer did at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366470,369056}But cuteness is only skin deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376772,379984}Lucifer… She loved doing\Nthings that people hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380401,383279}She always targeted\Nthe item I was planning to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383279,384989}She was like a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385907,387450}That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388409,390411}I've heard that somewhere before…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392788,395374}Although I don't have\Nany grudge against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395374,397752}you have to come along with me\Nso that I can get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398127,401255}Just curse the fates you were\Nborn as Lucifer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401881,403132}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403132,404759}Kabako?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.26,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:404759,407261}Kaba (hippopotamus) Ko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409388,410723}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410890,412725}Oh, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412725,415561}You're Ms. Kabako Sendo,\Nalso known as Rosemary, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415811,417313}I learned how to read\Nyour name from Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417521,420775}Please don't address me with\Nmy ridiculous real name! Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423069,426030}That horrible\Nwarning note from Lucifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:10.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426030,430576}Because of that, the public knew\Nmy real name and people made fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430576,431911}That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431911,433537}The humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433537,435957}I've never, even for a second,\Nforgotten that feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:20.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437166,440920}Like mother, like daughter!\NHow hateful! I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441504,443547}I didn't mean anything by it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443547,445508}I just wanted to know\Nabout the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446300,448970}The stolen items are not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449261,452640}We don't know anything\Nabout the items St. Tail stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452640,454183}Right, Maju?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454183,455685}Right, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455685,457478}{\i1}This mother and daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457478,458896}All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458896,460481}Sorry to have disturbed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462149,463651}Come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464568,467029}How infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467321,469365}I'm not afraid of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469782,471575}Who do they think they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471575,473244}Meimi, sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476789,480167}I checked for places where a pair\Nposing as mother and daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480167,482795}have moved in recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483254,484797}This is the only place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485423,487383}This is a monastery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:11.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487967,491137}Yes. It's the old building\Nalong the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491137,494348}It's not used now,\Nand it's supposed to be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494807,496726}It's been for sale\Nfor quite a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496726,500104}But people thought it was creepy\Nand didn't want to get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500104,503482}If those two are there,\Nthe stolen items must be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504358,506235}I'm going to get them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506235,509030}And I'll clear St. Tail's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:34.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510406,514994}{\i1}For the sake of Asuka Jr.,\Nwho believes in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:46.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522460,526630}{\i1}Darn it! Someone else\Nmust be using St. Tail's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527339,530092}{\i1}She must have been forced to be\Ninvolved in such a strange case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:55.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531719,535514}– That blimp!\N– Something is written on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:01.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537725,541479}"Tonight I'm going to the monastery\Nto take the rings and other riches
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541479,544774}of Kabako Sendo, also known\Nas Rosemary. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545649,547318}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547318,549153}It's St. Tail's warning note!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549528,550946}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553908,557328}I used the same\Nwarning note as my mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557328,558287}Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558287,559747}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559914,562500}Oh, you're worrying\Nabout the location, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562500,564919}Asuka Jr. can figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564919,566212}It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567880,570674}Is it wise to show her real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574512,576764}Oh, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:40.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576764,580643}I was only thinking about doing\Nthe same thing as my mom did…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590736,593072}She is indeed Lucifer's daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593072,595241}She has a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595449,598244}It doesn't matter whether\Nit's the mother or the daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598244,599620}I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602623,603707}Your money's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:06.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604458,606544}Thank… Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611215,614051}But who is Rosemary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:18.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614885,618013}Her last few messages\Nhave been difficult to understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621267,622935}What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623894,626689}I am Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626689,628899}How do you do, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630067,631569}You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635364,636824}Rosemary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:47.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643831,647084}This is jade dust…\NIt's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647835,649670}Don't take your eyes off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:54.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650921,654008}{\i1}What's happening?\NI can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674278,677281}You don't need to worry about\Nnot understanding what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677281,678782}Cute little detective…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:23.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679283,683037}I'm inviting you to my house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683037,686123}So what are you\Ngoing to do, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686123,688667}Your weak point is now in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:32.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689376,692171}You angered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692171,694882}You'll regret it,\Nand you'll wish you were dead.
Comment: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:37.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:697718,697718}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:42.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:702723,702723}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:53.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710105,713734}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718697,719740}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722117,723410}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725246,728249}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745641,747393}Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747768,750020}Don't worry. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752439,755943}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756235,757444}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:44.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761031,764243}I don't know why,\Nbut I have a bad feeling about this…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764868,765953}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857378,859713}{\i1}Asuka Jr. isn't here…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860506,862424}{\i1}Nor is his security staff…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862424,864468}{\i1}They couldn't find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868889,872059}{\i1}You… didn't come…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880901,883404}The item you're looking for\Nis in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:49.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884696,889368}But no matter how much you search,\Nthe detective won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891787,893288}Maju…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894248,896250}What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:57.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896917,897960}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898836,899670}You'll see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931535,933537}{\i1}Don't be misled, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933537,935247}{\i1}This is hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935247,937374}{\i1}It's an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940627,941295}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942754,943797}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945090,946258}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949970,951263}Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:11.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966945,971033}She created a wind with her magic\Nand pushed away my hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980459,982461}Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983128,985923}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987007,989218}Oh, weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989218,990719}You're in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990719,993263}Never mind that.\NLook this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993430,996725}Can you tell who is next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997392,999019}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001021,1004191}This is a one-way mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004191,1006527}They can't see us\Nfrom the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:52.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006902,1012324}You'd better watch closely from here\Nand see what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029258,1030425}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:14.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031343,1034429}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036014,1037766}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042896,1044189}It's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044982,1046483}Curtain ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055033,1056868}Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066503,1068714}What are you going to do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072134,1073218}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083604,1086732}I've gotten back\Neverything you stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088442,1089693}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090485,1092321}Please run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092696,1093864}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:27.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102623,1107419}Everyone has something that\Nthey don't want other people to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:31.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107419,1111214}You do, too, daughter of Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119431,1122100}That was loud.\NIt sounds like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122684,1124811}Don't worry, Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124811,1127564}There is always an end\Nto everything and every storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128065,1129441}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130317,1132527}There is an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153048,1155384}She's very near. Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:20.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156343,1160347}{\i1}I'll do the same to you, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180242,1183704}{\i1}Don't get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187541,1189626}{\i1}Not until I catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194297,1195424}{\i1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205142,1208687}You wanted to know\Nher identity, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214067,1215652}You're pleased, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239426,1241887}Why… Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:51.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247100,1251480}Haneoka!
